    "answer_id" : 43185019,
    "question_id" : 412380,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you do not need more than strings, you can use <a href=\"http://google.github.io/guava/releases/17.0/api/docs/com/google/common/io/Files.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">com.google.common.io.Files</a></p>\n\n<pre><code>Files.simplifyPath(\"some/prefix/with//extra///slashes\" + \"file//name\")\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>to get </p>\n\n<pre><code>\"some/prefix/with/extra/slashes/file/name\"\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
