  "title" : "How to combine paths in Java?",
  "body" : "<p>Is there a Java equivalent for <a href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/api/system.io.path.combine\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>System.IO.Path.Combine()</code></a> in C#/.NET? Or any code to accomplish this?</p>\n<p>This static method combines one or more strings into a path.</p>\n"
